<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>5679</hymn_number>
<author>mạhr fạyz, mạhr fạyz</author>
<title>mmtn lk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- mmtn lk wmạfysẖ klạm .. ywṣf msẖạʿr ạlạmtnạn
 wạlqlb fạḍ wsjd ạ̉mạm .. ḥbk yạ ạ̉b mlyạn ḥnạn
 ạlqrạr- yạ mwsyqạt ạlrwḥ kẖdyny
 wqdmyny tsẖkrạt
 lmn fdy̱ nfsy wsybyny
 ạ̉skb lh ṭyb ạltsbyḥạt
 2- mmtn lk ʿly̱ ạldẖbyḥ .. ạlly ạsẖtrạny bdm ạlfdạʾ
 wnẓm bṣrkẖạth ạlmdyḥ .. lrwḥya ạlmtʿbdẗ
 3- mmtn lk ʿly̱ ạlạ̉mạnẗ .. ạlly ṣnʿthạ mʿ ḥqạrty
 strtny bnʿmẗ wmʿwnẗ .. wạ̉ṣlḥt bạlnʿmẗ qytẖạrty
 4- mmtn lk ʿly̱ ʿmr ʿdy̱ .. bkl kẖyr ymly̱ ḥkạyạt
 wf kl wạḥdẗ mnhạ fyh sndẗ .. rfʿtny̱ lk bạltʿzyạt
 5- mmtn lk ʿly̱ ạlmḥbẗ .. ạlly ḥḍntny̱ byhạ f rḍạk
 ʿrft rwḥy trwḥ bṭlbẗ .. wthym bsẖwq nạḥyẗ lqạk
 6- mmtn lk wdmwʿy ḥmd .. lmʿạnhạ ʿrfạn bạljmyl
 tḥtyhạ bsmẗ ạ̹tsʿt bmjd .. ạ̹lh ḥnwn mạlhwsẖ mtẖyl</lyrics>
</song>